# Presentation talk track

Let me show this as a real-world troubleshooting story rather than just a list of metrics.

Assume we deployed a new version of a .NET service at 10:05 AM. Shortly after that, users started reporting slowness. The first thing we look at is the user-facing symptom: request latency. We can see p95 latency increasing after the deployment.

